#define GREETINGS ["Look, %s, I’m havin’ a real long day. Don't make it longer, okay?","Ain't ya got somewhere else to be, %s? Like, anywhere but here?","You’re makin’ me nervous, %s. Stay outta the way before I accidentally trip over ya.","I’m tryin’ to get some peace and quiet, %s. You're breakin’ the streak.","Go on, beat it, %s! I ain't in the mood for small talk.","You lookin' for trouble, %s? 'Cause I’m lookin' for a break, and it ain't workin' out.","Nice of ya to show up, I guess. Keep it quiet, %s.","Don’t ask me for a favor, %s. I’m already occupied.","Yeah, yeah, welcome, %s. Now, can we just get on with it?","You're standing kinda close, %s. Give a guy some space, willya?","You’re makin’ a lotta noise for someone your size, %s.","Alright, you’re here, %s. Don’t make me regret it.","I’ve seen tougher, %s. But I guess you’ll do for now.","Keep your eyes on the road, %s. I don't wanna be pickin' ya up off the floor.","You want something? Spit it out, %s, I’m busy.","You’re doin’ okay, %s. Just don’t get cocky.","Welcome to the neighborhood, %s. Try not to break anything, 'cause I'm the one who has to fix it.","You’re passable, %s. That’s high praise from me, so don't wear it out.","Just another day, just another face. Welcome, %s.","Whatever you're doin', %s, keep it professional.","Not bad, %s. You actually look like you know what you're doin'.","You’ve got potential, %s. Don't let it go to your head, though.","Okay, %s, you caught my attention. Make it worth it.","Finally, someone who ain't a total waste of space. Welcome, %s.","You holdin' your own pretty well, %s. Keep at it.","You pack a wallop, %s. I respect that—even if it is annoyin'.","I’ve seen a lot of strong types, %s. You’re definitely up there.","You want a sparring partner, %s? Give me an hour and I’ll think about it.","Watch the hands, %s. Those look like they could dent my exterior.","You got grit, %s. Reminds me of the old days.","Holy cow, %s! You're almost as tough as I am. Almost.","You’re a real heavy hitter, ain't ya, %s? Stay on my good side.","I’ve been lookin’ for a challenge. You lookin’ to trade blows, %s?","You're the real deal, aren't ya? Welcome, %s—just keep it down, okay?","Don't see power like that every day, %s. Glad you're on our side."]

#define WrestleWin ["Great. Another one. Beat it, %s, before I decide to turn ya into gravel.","Ain't you got somethin' better to do? Like, literally anything else? Scram, %s.","Don't bother standin' up, %s. You're just gonna get knocked down again anyway.","Keep this up and I'm gonna start chargin' for my time. Which you can't afford, %s.","Ugh. I needed a coffee, not a headache. Get lost, %s.","You're makin' a lot of noise for someone who's already lost, %s. Quiet down.","I'm gettin' too old for these pipsqueak fights. Go home, %s.","You call that a punch? My grandma hits harder, and she’s been gone for years, %s.","Don't look at me like that, %s. You walked into this, not me.","Go on, take your bruises and learn somethin'. Like stayin' away from me, %s.","You're persistent, I'll give ya that. But persistin' ain't the same as winnin', %s.","That's it? I thought maybe I'd actually work up a sweat today. Guess not, %s.","Keep it up and you'll eventually learn how to lose with some dignity, %s.","I'm still standin', and you're lookin' like a mess. Do the math, %s.","You're a nuisance, %s. A minor one, but a nuisance nonetheless.","Not bad, %s. Too bad for you it wasn't good enough.","I've had better days, and clearly, you've had worse. Move along, %s.","Ya got some fight in ya, but you're just gettin' in the way now, %s.","Don't feel bad. Everyone loses to the Thing eventually, %s.","Keep practiced, kid. You're gonna need it if you're gonna keep tryin' to scrap with me, %s.","You made me exert myself. That's annoyed me. Now beat it, %s.","You're good, %s, but I'm better. And I'm in a foul mood.","If you’re lookin' for a trophy for tryin', you're in the wrong place, %s.","I’m tired of scrapin' with people who don't know when to quit, %s.","You’re lucky I didn't break somethin' of yours. Now get outta here, %s.","Finally, a fight that wasn't a total waste of time. But I still won, %s.","Don't act all surprised, %s. I’m the Thing. What’d ya expect?","You’re tough, %s. But not tough enough to make me happy about this fight.","Take a seat and rethink your life choices, %s. You're out of your league.","Maybe next time bring a wreckin' ball, %s. You might stand a chance then.","Fine. You’re tough. Now are you gonna get up, or am I gonna have to drag ya out, %s?","That was almost fun. Almost. Now leave me alone, %s.","You’re a real piece of work, %s. But you're still on the floor.","Don't think just 'cause you're elite you can bother me all day, %s.","You lost, %s. Accept it, pack your bags, and quit naggin' me."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["That was a fluke! I slipped on a pebble! Don't push your luck, %s!","How'd that happen? I must've been distracted by somethin' important, %s.","Fine. You got me. Now don't make me regret it, %s.","You're kiddin' me, right? A total amateur beat me? This is a joke, %s.","Whatever. I’m tired anyway. Enjoy it, %s.","I ain't in the mood for this, %s. You caught me on a bad day.","Yeah, yeah, you won. Don't expect me to applaud, %s.","I’m gettin' soft in my old age, apparently. Don't let it happen again, %s.","You're lucky I was holdin' back, %s. Now shove off.","This is gonna be a long day, ain't it? Just go, %s.","Don't get cocky, %s. It was one fight, not a career.","You’re better than ya look, but don't think you're somethin' special, %s.","I’m gonna need a long break after this, %s. Thanks for nothin'.","Fine, you won. Now quit rubbin' it in, %s.","You're startin' to get on my nerves, %s. Consider yourself lucky.","You’re annoyingly good, %s. I don't like it.","I'm gonna be hearin' about this, ain't I? Thanks a lot, %s.","Fine, you bested me. Just stay out of my way now, %s.","You got a talent for bein' a pain in the neck, %s.","I'm not in the mood for a victory speech, %s. Go.","I'm irritated that you won, %s. I'm gonna go sulk now.","You’re tough, %s. And frankly, that's just annoyin'.","That’s the worst day I’ve had in ages, %s. You earned it, but I hated it.","You know how to push my buttons, %s. Keep it up and see what happens.","You're a real powerhouse, %s. I hate to admit it, but fine.","Great. Now I'm gonna be grumpy all day thanks to you, %s.","You got the better of me, %s. Don't think I'm happy about it.","You’re a real heavy hitter, %s. I hate that I had to lose to ya.","I respect ya, %s, but you're still a pain.","That was some serious scrap, %s. Now leave me to my misery.","I’m a force of nature, but you're a bigger nuisance, %s. You win.","It was an honor to go toe-to-toe with ya, but I'm still annoyed, %s.","You pushed me way past my limits, %s. Now quit lookin' at me.","You’re elite, %s. Doesn't mean I gotta like ya.","You've got grit, heart, and power—you’re the real deal, %s. Now go away."]
